Watch Jungle Perform “Busy Earnin'” and “Julia” on Late Night with Seth Meyers

posted by Graham on December 18, 2014 in News, Video

All seven members of Jungle stopped off at Late Night with Seth Meyers last night. It was probably a stark contrast to how they went into the holiday season last year—it’s been 12 months of firsts and debuts for Jungle, but these days they look plenty comfortable in the spotlight.

“Busy Earnin'” and “Julia” were chosen for last night. The band was decked out in their usual black and gold and Seth Meyers was, as usual, extremely pleased.
